# =============================================================================
# FORGE DROPSHIP — runtime config TEMPLATE (.env.example)
#
# HOW TO USE:
#   1. This is a template only. The REAL file next to it is  dropship.env
#   2. Copy this file:  cp dropship.env.example dropship.env  then edit values.
#   3. Redeploy (push.sh) so the box reloads. The real dropship.env is
#      git-ignored, lives OUTSIDE the web root, and must 404 over HTTP.
#
# FORGE DROPSHIP is the e-commerce / dropshipping workspace. Its agent crew
# (Midas the director + Hawk / Blaze / Otto) reads the store, proposes moves,
# and self-improves — but NEVER takes an outward action on its own. Launching an
# ad, placing/approving a supplier order, publishing a listing, or messaging a
# customer all stay your one-tap approval.
#
# SAFETY:
#   This folder is a SIBLING of the web app ("forge rei/"), so it lives OUTSIDE
#   the web-served dir. Nothing here is reachable over HTTP. Keys stay private.
# =============================================================================

# --- Shopify (store backbone) ------------------------------------------------
# Admin API access token from a custom app in your Shopify admin
# (Settings → Apps and sales channels → Develop apps). Scopes needed:
# read_orders, read_products, read_inventory (+ write_* later for gated actions).
SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN=your-store.myshopify.com
SHOPIFY_ADMIN_TOKEN=shpat_...
SHOPIFY_API_VERSION=2024-10

# --- AutoDS (sourcing + order automation) ------------------------------------
# API key from AutoDS (Settings → API). STORE_ID is the AutoDS store id.
AUTODS_API_KEY=
AUTODS_STORE_ID=

# --- Meta Ads (Facebook / Instagram) -----------------------------------------
# Reuses the same Meta pattern the agency side uses. Long-lived access token +
# a JSON map of {label: act_XXXXXXposit} ad-account ids.
META_ACCESS_TOKEN=
META_AD_ACCOUNT_MAP={}

# --- Anthropic (the crew's OWN Claude key) -----------------------------------
# Optional. If unset the crew FALLS BACK to the shared agency/wholesale key, so
# they work before a dedicated key is set. Placeholder values are ignored.
# DROPSHIP_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...

# --- Cadence + self-improvement (box loop knobs) -----------------------------
# Hours between Midas's autonomous operating-brief refreshes on the box. Set to 24
# so the crew doesn't burn Claude tokens on a timer when nothing changed; the manual
# "Learn from brain" / run-brief buttons still work on demand. Lower it if you want
# more frequent autonomous briefs (each brief is a paid Claude call).
FORGE_DROPSHIP_BRIEF_EVERY_H=24
# Briefs Midas must produce before an auto self-improve fires (so learn ≈ every
# LEARN_EVERY × BRIEF_EVERY_H hours). The manual learn button ignores this.
FORGE_DROPSHIP_LEARN_EVERY=8
# Minimum minutes between self-improvement writes (rate guard).
FORGE_DROPSHIP_LEARN_GAP_MIN=45

# --- Obsidian brain (vault) --------------------------------------------------
# Optional override for the Agentic-OS Obsidian vault path. The crew reads their
# learned playbooks from <vault>/Skills/<agent>-playbook.md in addition to the
# local skills/ seeds in this folder.
# FORGE_VAULT=/Users/yg4st/Desktop/Agentic-OS/vault

# =============================================================================
# NOT WIRED YET — add-key stubs. Drop a value here and the matching integration
# lights up on the next deploy; until then that channel reads mock / "add key".
# =============================================================================
# --- PiPiAds (trending-product / ad-spy signal — powers Product Watch) --------
# The "watch new trending things" source: real winning TikTok/FB products + TikTok
# Shop revenue trend, so Hawk scores products that are ACTUALLY moving instead of
# guesses. Get the API key + billing at https://www.pipispy.com/ . Routes are
# env-overridable (confirm against your plan's API docs before first pull):
# PIPIADS_API_KEY=
# PIPIADS_API_BASE=https://open.pipiads.com
# PIPIADS_TRENDING_PATH=/api/v1/products/trending
# PIPIADS_SEARCH_PATH=/api/v1/products/search
# PIPIADS_AUTH_HEADER=Authorization
# --- MCP servers (Connections & MCP tab) -------------------------------------
# The dashboard talks to MCP servers over Streamable HTTP. A server's URL is edited
# in the Connections & MCP tab; these env vars are the DEFAULTS it starts from, and
# any token stays HERE — the UI only ever references a variable NAME, never a value.
#
# Shopify Storefront MCP: your store's own endpoint (catalog, cart, policies). Left
# blank it is derived from SHOPIFY_STORE_DOMAIN above as https://<domain>/api/mcp.
# SHOPIFY_STOREFRONT_MCP_URL=
#
# AutoDS MCP: paste the URL when you have it, then hit Probe in the Connections tab —
# the real tool list loads from the server itself, no redeploy. Sourcing reads keep
# working over the REST bridge (AUTODS_API_KEY above) meanwhile.
# AUTODS_MCP_URL=
# AUTODS_MCP_TOKEN=
#
# (The Shopify Dev MCP — `npx -y @shopify/dev-mcp@latest` — is a stdio server. It runs
# in your Claude/operator session; the box cannot reach it, so it is listed in the tab
# for reference only and never shows as "connected".)

# --- AutoDS Marketplace (Product Finding Hub — winning products) --------------
# Uses your existing AUTODS_API_KEY above. The marketplace/finder is a PAID AutoDS
# add-on and may not be on every tier's API — confirm the path, then set it:
# AUTODS_MARKETPLACE_PATH=/marketplace/products/
# --- TikTok (Ads / TikTok Shop) ----------------------------------------------
# TIKTOK_ACCESS_TOKEN=
# TIKTOK_ADVERTISER_ID=
# TIKTOK_SHOP_ID=
# --- Klaviyo (email / SMS marketing) -----------------------------------------
# KLAVIYO_API_KEY=
# --- Google Analytics 4 ------------------------------------------------------
# GA4_PROPERTY_ID=
# GA4_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_JSON=
# --- Shipment tracking -------------------------------------------------------
# AFTERSHIP_API_KEY=
# --- GoHighLevel (own sub-account — customer SMS, owner-initiated only) -------
# GHL_API_KEY=
# GHL_LOCATION_ID=
# --- Higgsfield (ad video / image creative) ----------------------------------
# HIGGSFIELD_API_KEY=
# HIGGSFIELD_API_SECRET=
# --- Metricool (social scheduling) -------------------------------------------
# METRICOOL_USER_TOKEN=
